<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">Our customers love us, but we can&rsquo;t claim all of the credit&mdash;let&rsquo;s face it, the sun does most of the work to power their homes!</p>
