<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 25px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">Wayne looked into getting solar panels 5 or 10 years ago but found it to be cost-prohibitive. Then, he says, he heard a commercial on the radio that was a turning point in his decision to go solar. It was not only a matter of dollars.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">Wayne very much supports the collective effort of using energy efficiently and furthering independence from foreign oil. Ultimately, it&rsquo;s free money and free energy, he believes.</p>
<p style="font-size: 21px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 10px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #e45206; font-style: italic;">&ldquo;If a lot of us did this, what a big difference we could all make.&rdquo;</p>
